dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"西餐食魚唔可以反 要用刀切走骨頭 細細個就要學 好麻煩"},{"pid":"373b3f3d51156763734d0a910d14b04f16802d28","tid":958876,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"紅酒汁點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17aa628c78295272531e87e7ba803facab3fcb3d","tid":958876,"uid":45431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d96edd601278b1cc0bd464e6ce6f6382db737320","tid":958876,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"西餐食魚唔可以反 要用刀切走骨頭 細細個就要學 好麻煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T10:56:05.000Z","msg":"中餐咪一樣，去頭去尾<br />\n食左個面，把刀插入中間打橫拉過去就成條骨起<br />\n不過講真，鬼佬有幾可食原條魚"},{"pid":"7567399af0d8142b4ff25cc04cbd36ed842bdbcb","tid":958876,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e74c09524fe752394435e9b4437c7a7e5e6e36c7","tid":958876,"uid":204380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:03:28.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"451e8293f4d8e3a5751cb9c00b58648823e63665","tid":958876,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069a4cf2ac45e430d2a57e89b6de5a080f8106dd","tid":958876,"uid":68594,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9354511c36d59e7ff4d4edb1635474b5eb35ab7c","tid":958876,"uid":44646,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"幾時應該同侍應講GOOD JOB？幾時用WELL DONE？<br />\n一直分唔清楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"好啦，我唯有認真咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實牛扒嘅成數係5種，分別係：<br />\nrare=1成熟<br />\nmedium rare=3成熟<br />\nmedium\t=5成熟<br />\nmedium well=7成熟<br />\nwell done=全熟<br />\n<br />\n仲有！記得係無雙數！無雙數！無雙數！<br />\n因為好重要！所以要講三次！<br />\n<br />\n牛扒係冇八成熟嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，你同佢講good job，佢會同你講句thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba915412abae6b5f179c4012a00312c865ccb597","tid":958876,"uid":68594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2007f9c4b64c78527f6f5dc0a1a651310f9f7199","tid":958876,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T08:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"其實如果你想健康啲，反而唔係唔用牛油，係用另一種牛奶，可能用脫脂奶，因為本身牛油已經有足夠嘅脂肪，所以如果用脫脂奶嘅感覺唔會差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}